/ %section.intro
/   %h3 What Is Telescope?        
/   %p 
/     Telescope is an open-source app that lets you easily set up your own online community. 
/     It's built with <a href="http://meteor.com" target="_blank">Meteor</a>, a real-time Javascript framework, and you can use it to create your own discussion board, social news site (like <a href="http://news.ycombinator.com" target="_blank">Hacker News</a> or <a href="http://reddit.com">Reddit</a>), or collaboration space.


